article.headline: Fairfield wins 77-68 over Manhattan

images.caption: Manhattan Jaspers vs. Fairfield Stags: Game Highlights

article.story: FAIRFIELD, Conn. -- — Jalen Leach had 23 points in Fairfield's 77-68 win against Manhattan on Sunday. Leach also added six rebounds for the Stags (13-9, 7-4 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Caleb Fields shot 6 for 12 (3 for 7 from 3-point range) and 4 of 4 from the free-throw line to add 19 points. Brycen Goodine was 8-of-12 shooting (2 for 5 from 3-point range) to finish with 18 points. Jaden Winston led the way for the Jaspers (5-15, 2-9) with 18 points, nine rebounds and six assists. Daniel Rouzan added 11 points and five assists for Manhattan. Perry Cowan also had 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
